title: Silence of the Rams
description:
Mina talks to Steven Ruiz of The Ringer about the Jets naming Joe Flacco as their starter, the offensive woes of the Rams in the past couple of weeks, what the Eagles do or do not have in Jalen Hurts, Cam Newton's return to Carolina, and what to expect when the Chiefs host the Cowboys.
